1
00:00:02,293 --> 00:00:05,130
<font color="japanese">（アノス）カノン
2000年前に何があった？</c.japanese>

2
00:00:05,547 --> 00:00:07,424
<font color="japanese">（レイ）君が言ったとおりだ</c.japanese>

3
00:00:07,841 --> 00:00:10,552
<font color="japanese">人間は弱かったよ アノス</c.japanese>

4
00:00:14,973 --> 00:00:18,768
<font color="japanese">僕は ジェルガ先生の
賛同者に殺された</c.japanese>

5
00:00:19,269 --> 00:00:21,354
<font color="japanese">そして 彼らは君を―</c.japanese>

6
00:00:21,479 --> 00:00:24,274
<font color="japanese">2000年後に滅ぼす計画を
立てたんだ</c.japanese>

7
00:00:25,316 --> 00:00:29,029
<font color="japanese">あまりに理不尽な人間の過ちだ</c.japanese>

8
00:00:29,487 --> 00:00:32,157
<font color="japanese">僕は それを
正さなければならなかった</c.japanese>

9
00:00:32,532 --> 00:00:33,950
<font color="japanese">エヴァンスマナは―</c.japanese>

10
00:00:34,075 --> 00:00:37,328
<font color="japanese">定められた宿命さえも
断ち切る力を持つ</c.japanese>

11
00:00:40,915 --> 00:00:43,877
<font color="japanese">君が暴虐の魔王として
転生する宿命を―</c.japanese>

12
00:00:44,377 --> 00:00:45,628
<font color="japanese">僕は断ち切ったんだ</c.japanese>

13
00:00:47,672 --> 00:00:51,259
<font color="japanese">（アノス）それで 俺の名は
忘れられたということか</c.japanese>

14
00:00:52,844 --> 00:00:57,057
<font color="japanese">（レイ）時間をかけて 歴史は
少しずつ書き換わっていったよ</c.japanese>

15
00:00:57,474 --> 00:00:58,516
<font color="japanese">そして―</c.japanese>

16
00:00:58,641 --> 00:01:02,062
<font color="japanese">架空の魔王 アヴォス･
ディルヘヴィアが誕生した</c.japanese>

17
00:01:02,937 --> 00:01:05,523
<font color="japanese">君に気付かれるとは
思わなかったけどね</c.japanese>

18
00:01:05,774 --> 00:01:08,109
<font color="japanese">（アノス）お前は
討たれるつもりなのだな</c.japanese>

19
00:01:08,401 --> 00:01:10,945
<font color="japanese">暴虐の魔王として 人間に</c.japanese>

20
00:01:11,571 --> 00:01:14,491
<font color="japanese">人間は どこまでも魔族を殺す</c.japanese>

21
00:01:15,241 --> 00:01:19,287
<font color="japanese">いつか君は 人間を殺すしか
道がなくなる</c.japanese>

22
00:01:19,412 --> 00:01:21,289
<font color="japanese">2000年前のように</c.japanese>

23
00:01:21,790 --> 00:01:24,459
<font color="japanese">誰よりも平和を望んだ君が</c.japanese>

24
00:01:25,794 --> 00:01:27,337
<font color="japanese">全ての元凶は</c.japanese>

25
00:01:27,462 --> 00:01:30,715
<font color="japanese">ジェルガ先生がアスクに込めた
魔王への憎悪</c.japanese>

26
00:01:31,758 --> 00:01:35,595
<font color="japanese">アヴォス･ディルヘヴィアが
滅びれば その呪いは消えるはずだ</c.japanese>

27
00:01:36,304 --> 00:01:38,389
<font color="japanese">（アノス）
人間に殺された お前が―</c.japanese>

28
00:01:38,765 --> 00:01:41,309
<font color="japanese">我が身を犠牲にしてまで
することか？</c.japanese>

29
00:01:41,684 --> 00:01:43,728
<font color="japanese">（レイ）それでも僕は信じたい</c.japanese>

30
00:01:44,062 --> 00:01:45,563
<font color="japanese">僕は勇者だ</c.japanese>

31
00:01:45,688 --> 00:01:48,358
<font color="japanese">人々の過ちを償う義務がある</c.japanese>

32
00:01:48,775 --> 00:01:52,529
<font color="japanese">君は約束どおり
命を懸けて平和を作った</c.japanese>

33
00:01:52,654 --> 00:01:53,780
<font color="japanese">すばらしい</c.japanese>

34
00:01:53,905 --> 00:01:56,157
<font color="japanese">本当に すばらしい世界になったよ</c.japanese>

35
00:01:56,699 --> 00:01:59,536
<font color="japanese">だけど 魔王アノス</c.japanese>

36
00:01:59,869 --> 00:02:01,871
<font color="japanese">俺は まだ見せていない</c.japanese>

37
00:02:01,996 --> 00:02:03,540
<font color="japanese">人の優しさを</c.japanese>

38
00:02:03,665 --> 00:02:06,042
<font color="japanese">お前が望んだ本当の平和を</c.japanese>

39
00:02:08,044 --> 00:02:12,674
<font color="japanese">（アノス）2000年前
死地へ赴く人間の恋人たちは―</c.japanese>

40
00:02:12,799 --> 00:02:15,093
<font color="japanese">生まれ変わっても結ばれるように</c.japanese>

41
00:02:15,218 --> 00:02:18,471
<font color="japanese">聖なる貝の殻を２つに分けて
首飾りを作り</c.japanese>

42
00:02:18,596 --> 00:02:20,098
<font color="japanese">互いにつけた</c.japanese>

43
00:02:20,431 --> 00:02:23,351
<font color="japanese">これは お前にとって
ミシェンスの首飾り</c.japanese>

44
00:02:24,102 --> 00:02:27,397
<font color="japanese">愛する者に 別れを
告げてきたというわけだ</c.japanese>

45
00:02:29,566 --> 00:02:32,819
<font color="japanese">長きにわたり お前は
壮大な準備をしてきた</c.japanese>

46
00:02:33,486 --> 00:02:36,072
<font color="japanese">いまさら言葉では揺らぎはしまい</c.japanese>

47
00:02:36,531 --> 00:02:40,493
<font color="japanese">これを返してほしくば
力ずくで奪ってみよ</c.japanese>

48
00:02:40,743 --> 00:02:43,037
<font color="japanese">（レイ）そう言うと思ったよ</c.japanese>

49
00:02:44,330 --> 00:02:47,041
<font color="japanese">いかせてもらう 君を守るために</c.japanese>

50
00:02:47,333 --> 00:02:50,962
<font color="japanese">いかせはせぬ お前を守るために</c.japanese>

51
00:02:51,462 --> 00:02:55,884
<font color="japanese">♪～</c.japanese>

52
00:04:15,922 --> 00:04:20,927
{\an8}<font color="japanese">～♪</c.japanese>

53
00:04:21,719 --> 00:04:24,222
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（レイ）うおーっ！</c.japanese>

54
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:30,812
<font color="japanese">ギア･グレアス</c.japanese>

55
00:04:32,939 --> 00:04:33,940
<font color="japanese">はあっ！</c.japanese>

56
00:04:36,401 --> 00:04:38,319
<font color="japanese">（レイ）勇者なんて幻想だ</c.japanese>

57
00:04:41,155 --> 00:04:41,990
<font color="japanese">１つ</c.japanese>

58
00:04:43,741 --> 00:04:46,327
<font color="japanese">（レイ）僕は そんな人を
一度も見たことがない</c.japanese>

59
00:04:46,577 --> 00:04:47,578
<font color="japanese">ベブズド</c.japanese>

60
00:04:48,413 --> 00:04:49,247
<font color="japanese">２つ</c.japanese>

61
00:04:50,707 --> 00:04:51,666
<font color="japanese">がはっ…</c.japanese>

62
00:04:52,292 --> 00:04:55,044
<font color="japanese">（レイ）本当は殺したくなかった</c.japanese>

63
00:04:56,296 --> 00:04:57,547
<font color="japanese">リオ･エドラム</c.japanese>

64
00:05:00,717 --> 00:05:01,551
<font color="japanese">（レイ）くっ…</c.japanese>

65
00:05:03,594 --> 00:05:04,595
<font color="japanese">うわあっ！</c.japanese>

66
00:05:04,721 --> 00:05:07,640
<font color="japanese">（レイ）それでも
人々の希望に責めたてられ</c.japanese>

67
00:05:08,141 --> 00:05:09,100
<font color="japanese">３つ</c.japanese>

68
00:05:10,768 --> 00:05:14,063
<font color="japanese">（レイ）こぼれていく命に
目を覆いながら</c.japanese>

69
00:05:14,272 --> 00:05:15,440
<font color="japanese">ジオ･グレイズ</c.japanese>

70
00:05:15,732 --> 00:05:16,566
<font color="japanese">（レイ）ぐあっ！</c.japanese>

71
00:05:16,691 --> 00:05:18,318
<font color="japanese">（レイ）終わらない
この地獄の底で―</c.japanese>

72
00:05:19,527 --> 00:05:21,779
<font color="japanese">滅びるまで戦い続けるしかなかった</c.japanese>

73
00:05:23,072 --> 00:05:24,615
<font color="japanese">（アノス）４つ ５つ</c.japanese>

74
00:05:24,741 --> 00:05:25,658
<font color="japanese">（レイ）だけど…</c.japanese>

75
00:05:27,535 --> 00:05:29,162
<font color="japanese">うおーっ！</c.japanese>

76
00:05:29,495 --> 00:05:30,330
<font color="japanese">がっ…</c.japanese>

77
00:05:31,914 --> 00:05:34,250
<font color="japanese">お前の根源は残り１つだ</c.japanese>

78
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:35,335
<font color="japanese">（レイ）ぐっ…</c.japanese>

79
00:05:43,342 --> 00:05:45,470
<font color="japanese">お前に勝ち目はない</c.japanese>

80
00:05:47,764 --> 00:05:49,974
<font color="japanese">（レイ）何度 負けても―</c.japanese>

81
00:05:50,099 --> 00:05:52,310
<font color="japanese">最後に一度 勝てばいい</c.japanese>

82
00:05:53,269 --> 00:05:54,353
<font color="japanese">いつか―</c.japanese>

83
00:05:54,479 --> 00:05:58,566
<font color="japanese">平和のために命を懸けるべきは
今じゃないって―</c.japanese>

84
00:05:58,691 --> 00:06:00,276
<font color="japanese">そう思ってた</c.japanese>

85
00:06:00,568 --> 00:06:01,694
<font color="japanese">でも違う！</c.japanese>

86
00:06:04,322 --> 00:06:06,699
<font color="japanese">目の前に救うべき人がいる</c.japanese>

87
00:06:06,824 --> 00:06:09,368
<font color="japanese">いつかなんて もう待てない！</c.japanese>

88
00:06:11,412 --> 00:06:15,083
<font color="japanese">今 １人でも多く
苦しんでいる人を助けたい</c.japanese>

89
00:06:16,209 --> 00:06:17,877
<font color="japanese">そう思えないのなら</c.japanese>

90
00:06:18,002 --> 00:06:19,504
<font color="japanese">僕は いつかが来たって―</c.japanese>

91
00:06:19,962 --> 00:06:22,173
<font color="japanese">誰も救えやしない！</c.japanese>

92
00:06:25,343 --> 00:06:27,011
<font color="japanese">うおおー！</c.japanese>

93
00:06:36,854 --> 00:06:38,773
<font color="japanese">はあーっ！</c.japanese>

94
00:06:40,691 --> 00:06:41,567
<font color="japanese">ハッ…</c.japanese>

95
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:46,322
<font color="japanese">本当にやっかいな男だ お前は</c.japanese>

96
00:07:00,711 --> 00:07:01,712
<font color="japanese">あ…</c.japanese>

97
00:07:09,345 --> 00:07:11,472
<font color="japanese">（一同のざわめき）</c.japanese>

98
00:07:13,224 --> 00:07:14,600
<font color="japanese">（一同のざわめき）</c.japanese>

99
00:07:14,725 --> 00:07:16,060
<font color="japanese">（エリオ）アヴォス様！</c.japanese>

100
00:07:16,269 --> 00:07:17,145
<font color="japanese">（サーシャ）ああっ…</c.japanese>

101
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,104
<font color="japanese">（ミーシャ）アノス…</c.japanese>

102
00:07:18,438 --> 00:07:19,439
<font color="japanese">（ミサ）あ…</c.japanese>

103
00:07:19,689 --> 00:07:22,650
<font color="japanese">（勇者兵）暴虐の魔王が！
（勇者兵）見ろ あの剣！</c.japanese>

104
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,610
<font color="japanese">（勇者兵）エヴァンスマナ！</c.japanese>

105
00:07:24,861 --> 00:07:26,612
<font color="japanese">あの聖なる力は…</c.japanese>

106
00:07:26,737 --> 00:07:28,364
<font color="japanese">（勇者兵）勇者カノン…</c.japanese>

107
00:07:29,949 --> 00:07:32,118
<font color="japanese">（アノス）そんな顔をするな</c.japanese>

108
00:07:32,243 --> 00:07:34,078
<font color="japanese">勇者らしくもない</c.japanese>

109
00:07:34,203 --> 00:07:35,455
<font color="japanese">どうして…</c.japanese>

110
00:07:36,747 --> 00:07:38,958
<font color="japanese">（アノス）お前の筋書きどおりだ</c.japanese>

111
00:07:39,083 --> 00:07:41,627
<font color="japanese">これで人間の憎しみも晴れる</c.japanese>

112
00:07:43,004 --> 00:07:45,631
<font color="japanese">同胞たちよ 全軍撤退せよ！</c.japanese>

113
00:07:46,716 --> 00:07:49,594
<font color="japanese">余が再び
この地に転生するまで―</c.japanese>

114
00:07:49,719 --> 00:07:51,596
<font color="japanese">人間への報復は許さぬ</c.japanese>

115
00:07:53,139 --> 00:07:54,390
<font color="japanese">生きよ！</c.japanese>

116
00:07:54,765 --> 00:07:57,310
<font color="japanese">魔王が戻る その日まで！</c.japanese>

117
00:08:01,647 --> 00:08:04,275
<font color="japanese">（レイ）終わらない
この地獄の底で―</c.japanese>

118
00:08:04,484 --> 00:08:07,570
<font color="japanese">滅びるまで戦い続けるしかなかった</c.japanese>

119
00:08:07,904 --> 00:08:09,030
<font color="japanese">だけど―</c.japanese>

120
00:08:09,530 --> 00:08:13,784
<font color="japanese">今も昔も 最後に手を
差し伸べてくれたのは…</c.japanese>

121
00:08:17,955 --> 00:08:19,165
<font color="japanese">アノス…</c.japanese>

122
00:08:19,665 --> 00:08:20,958
<font color="japanese">君だった</c.japanese>

123
00:08:21,459 --> 00:08:24,212
<font color="japanese">君が… 君こそが―</c.japanese>

124
00:08:25,004 --> 00:08:27,715
<font color="japanese">僕の たった１人の勇者だった</c.japanese>

125
00:08:53,491 --> 00:08:55,117
<font color="japanese">（レイ）魔王は滅びた</c.japanese>

126
00:08:55,576 --> 00:08:57,828
<font color="japanese">争いは これで終わりだ！</c.japanese>

127
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:09,006
<font color="japanese">（エリオ）撤退せよ</c.japanese>

128
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:12,552
<font color="japanese">ディルヘイドにて
魔王様の帰りを待つ！</c.japanese>

129
00:09:12,677 --> 00:09:14,428
<font color="japanese">（ディエゴ）ぐぐぐ…</c.japanese>

130
00:09:14,554 --> 00:09:16,055
<font color="japanese">だまされるな！</c.japanese>

131
00:09:16,514 --> 00:09:19,100
<font color="japanese">やつは勇者カノンではない</c.japanese>

132
00:09:19,225 --> 00:09:20,393
<font color="japanese">魔族だ！</c.japanese>

133
00:09:20,518 --> 00:09:23,771
<font color="japanese">魔族は殺せ！</c.japanese>

134
00:09:24,605 --> 00:09:28,192
<font color="japanese">１万のゼシア兵よ 自爆せよ</c.japanese>

135
00:09:28,484 --> 00:09:31,070
<font color="japanese">魔族どもを滅ぼすのだ！</c.japanese>

136
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,908
<font color="japanese">（ディエゴ）フフフ…</c.japanese>

137
00:09:36,033 --> 00:09:37,201
<font color="japanese">（エレオノール）やめて！</c.japanese>

138
00:09:38,452 --> 00:09:39,704
<font color="japanese">全部 終わったんだ</c.japanese>

139
00:09:40,079 --> 00:09:42,290
<font color="japanese">もう戦う理由なんてないはずだぞ</c.japanese>

140
00:09:42,498 --> 00:09:45,876
<font color="japanese">黙れ！　これは正義の行いだ</c.japanese>

141
00:09:46,002 --> 00:09:50,047
<font color="japanese">俺たち人間から全てを奪った
魔族どもへ下す―</c.japanese>

142
00:09:50,172 --> 00:09:50,590
<font color="japanese">鉄ついなのだ！</c.japanese>

143
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:52,341
<font color="japanese">鉄ついなのだ！</c.japanese>

144
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:52,341
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">そうだ 殺せ…</c.japanese>

145
00:09:53,509 --> 00:09:56,846
<font color="japanese">（エレオノール）違う！
あなたは何も奪われてなんかない</c.japanese>

146
00:09:56,971 --> 00:09:59,390
<font color="japanese">その憎悪は あなたのものじゃない</c.japanese>

147
00:09:59,557 --> 00:10:00,683
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">今が結実のとき</c.japanese>

148
00:10:00,683 --> 00:10:02,101
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">今が結実のとき</c.japanese>

149
00:10:00,683 --> 00:10:02,101
<font color="japanese">（ディエゴ）
黙れ 黙れ 黙れ 黙れ 黙れ！</c.japanese>

150
00:10:02,101 --> 00:10:05,354
<font color="japanese">（ディエゴ）
黙れ 黙れ 黙れ 黙れ 黙れ！</c.japanese>

151
00:10:05,563 --> 00:10:07,273
<font color="japanese">たった１人の死で</c.japanese>

152
00:10:07,398 --> 00:10:10,610
<font color="japanese">2000年の憎しみが
収まるものか！</c.japanese>

153
00:10:10,735 --> 00:10:13,321
<font color="japanese">この世界から魔族が滅びるまで</c.japanese>

154
00:10:13,529 --> 00:10:17,283
<font color="japanese">１人残らず たたき潰し
殺し尽くすまで</c.japanese>

155
00:10:17,408 --> 00:10:19,619
<font color="japanese">戦争は終わらんのだ！</c.japanese>

156
00:10:20,411 --> 00:10:24,832
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）殺せ 殺せ
殺せ 殺せ 殺せ…</c.japanese>

157
00:10:24,957 --> 00:10:26,000
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（勇者兵）殺せ 殺せ…</c.japanese>

158
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,585
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（勇者兵）殺せ 殺せ…</c.japanese>

159
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,585
<font color="japanese">殺せ</c.japanese>

160
00:10:28,002 --> 00:10:29,545
<font color="japanese">魔族を殺せ</c.japanese>

161
00:10:30,046 --> 00:10:32,798
<font color="japanese">殺せ 殺せ 殺せ…</c.japanese>

162
00:10:33,341 --> 00:10:35,217
<font color="japanese">これは… アスク？</c.japanese>

163
00:10:35,635 --> 00:10:38,971
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）
魔族を滅ぼす聖なる魔法</c.japanese>

164
00:10:39,096 --> 00:10:40,431
<font color="japanese">我が名はジェルガ</c.japanese>

165
00:10:40,723 --> 00:10:41,891
<font color="japanese">（レイ）先生…</c.japanese>

166
00:10:42,266 --> 00:10:43,643
<font color="japanese">ジェルガ総帥…</c.japanese>

167
00:10:43,976 --> 00:10:45,311
<font color="japanese">残念だよ</c.japanese>

168
00:10:45,436 --> 00:10:49,398
<font color="japanese">勇者である お前が
汚れた魔族に転生しようとはな</c.japanese>

169
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:51,817
<font color="japanese">（レイ）僕も残念です</c.japanese>

170
00:10:52,068 --> 00:10:54,236
<font color="japanese">あなたは人であることすら捨て―</c.japanese>

171
00:10:54,362 --> 00:10:57,615
<font color="japanese">ただ魔族を滅ぼすだけの魔法に
成り果ててしまった</c.japanese>

172
00:10:59,075 --> 00:11:00,576
<font color="japanese">僕が断ち切ります</c.japanese>

173
00:11:00,701 --> 00:11:02,244
<font color="japanese">その憎しみと共に！</c.japanese>

174
00:11:02,912 --> 00:11:05,206
<font color="japanese">この身は真に聖なる魔法</c.japanese>

175
00:11:05,331 --> 00:11:07,333
<font color="japanese">聖剣で滅ぼすことはできない</c.japanese>

176
00:11:07,458 --> 00:11:08,292
<font color="japanese">（レイ）くっ…</c.japanese>

177
00:11:08,459 --> 00:11:11,962
<font color="japanese">これが魔族断罪の魔法
“ジェルガ”だ</c.japanese>

178
00:11:12,088 --> 00:11:14,548
<font color="japanese">（サーシャ）あなたに
裁かれる いわれはないわ</c.japanese>

179
00:11:14,673 --> 00:11:17,093
<font color="japanese">主を失った あわれな配下か</c.japanese>

180
00:11:17,218 --> 00:11:18,636
<font color="japanese">おあいにくさま</c.japanese>

181
00:11:18,761 --> 00:11:20,679
<font color="japanese">私たちは信じてるの</c.japanese>

182
00:11:20,805 --> 00:11:22,431
<font color="japanese">アノスは帰ってくる</c.japanese>

183
00:11:22,890 --> 00:11:25,059
<font color="japanese">（アイヴィス）我が直系にして</c.japanese>

184
00:11:25,184 --> 00:11:29,021
<font color="japanese">暴虐の魔王の寵愛を受けし双つ子よ</c.japanese>

185
00:11:29,271 --> 00:11:32,900
<font color="japanese">我らネクロンの秘術を
見せるべきときが来た</c.japanese>

186
00:11:35,277 --> 00:11:36,112
<font color="japanese">怖くない</c.japanese>

187
00:11:36,445 --> 00:11:37,571
<font color="japanese">当たり前だわ</c.japanese>

188
00:11:38,406 --> 00:11:39,907
<font color="japanese">（ミーシャ）私は あなた</c.japanese>

189
00:11:40,032 --> 00:11:41,450
<font color="japanese">（サーシャ）あなたは 私ね</c.japanese>

190
00:11:41,826 --> 00:11:44,370
<font color="japanese">（アイヴィス）
正しき姿に戻るがよい</c.japanese>

191
00:11:46,247 --> 00:11:47,832
<font color="japanese">（２人）ディノ･ジクセス！</c.japanese>

192
00:11:58,884 --> 00:12:00,136
<font color="japanese">こざかしい</c.japanese>

193
00:12:01,011 --> 00:12:02,596
<font color="japanese">（ミーシャ）アノスは必ず来る</c.japanese>

194
00:12:02,721 --> 00:12:03,973
<font color="japanese">あなたを倒しに</c.japanese>

195
00:12:04,098 --> 00:12:06,016
<font color="japanese">（サーシャ）
根源を滅ぼしたくらいで―</c.japanese>

196
00:12:06,684 --> 00:12:09,478
<font color="japanese">私の魔王様が
死ぬわけないんだから！</c.japanese>

197
00:12:09,603 --> 00:12:11,021
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）クハハハ！</c.japanese>

198
00:12:11,188 --> 00:12:14,108
<font color="japanese">とうとう常識すら
理解できぬようになったか</c.japanese>

199
00:12:14,233 --> 00:12:15,818
<font color="japanese">あわれな魔族よ</c.japanese>

200
00:12:15,943 --> 00:12:19,280
<font color="japanese">ならば さらなる絶望を
味わわせてやろう</c.japanese>

201
00:12:23,117 --> 00:12:24,368
<font color="japanese">自爆しろ</c.japanese>

202
00:12:24,577 --> 00:12:25,578
<font color="japanese">（アイシャ）させない！</c.japanese>

203
00:12:28,873 --> 00:12:29,874
<font color="japanese">ゼシア！</c.japanese>

204
00:12:33,294 --> 00:12:34,295
<font color="japanese">レイさん</c.japanese>

205
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:35,379
<font color="japanese">（レイ）止めるよ</c.japanese>

206
00:12:37,423 --> 00:12:38,257
<font color="japanese">フスカ！</c.japanese>

207
00:12:39,467 --> 00:12:40,468
<font color="japanese">（レイ）はあっ！</c.japanese>

208
00:12:45,556 --> 00:12:46,390
<font color="japanese">（エリオ）ならん！</c.japanese>

209
00:12:46,974 --> 00:12:48,058
<font color="japanese">（エレオノール）ダメだぞ！</c.japanese>

210
00:12:49,477 --> 00:12:50,311
<font color="japanese">ゼシア！</c.japanese>

211
00:12:52,438 --> 00:12:53,606
<font color="japanese">止まって</c.japanese>

212
00:12:53,731 --> 00:12:54,565
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）フン</c.japanese>

213
00:12:56,734 --> 00:12:59,028
<font color="japanese">フフフ…</c.japanese>

214
00:13:01,071 --> 00:13:01,906
<font color="japanese">まだ！</c.japanese>

215
00:13:03,157 --> 00:13:04,408
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）無駄だ</c.japanese>

216
00:13:08,204 --> 00:13:09,038
<font color="japanese">くっ…</c.japanese>

217
00:13:13,292 --> 00:13:14,418
<font color="japanese">間に合わない！</c.japanese>

218
00:13:16,795 --> 00:13:19,381
<font color="japanese">フハハハハ！</c.japanese>

219
00:13:20,174 --> 00:13:22,176
<font color="japanese">ゼシアー！</c.japanese>

220
00:13:22,343 --> 00:13:23,886
<font color="japanese">もうダメ…</c.japanese>

221
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:37,983
<font color="japanese">（アノス）ご苦労だった</c.japanese>

222
00:13:38,526 --> 00:13:40,236
<font color="japanese">よく持ちこたえたな</c.japanese>

223
00:13:40,486 --> 00:13:41,487
<font color="japanese">（アイシャ）アノス！</c.japanese>

224
00:13:41,779 --> 00:13:43,739
<font color="japanese">な… 何の悪夢だ！</c.japanese>

225
00:13:44,031 --> 00:13:48,452
<font color="japanese">根源が滅んだくらいで
俺が よみがえらぬと思ったか</c.japanese>

226
00:13:48,661 --> 00:13:51,455
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）
世の摂理に反している！</c.japanese>

227
00:13:51,622 --> 00:13:53,999
<font color="japanese">起源魔法アグロネムト</c.japanese>

228
00:13:54,124 --> 00:13:57,545
<font color="japanese">敵の攻撃を起源とし
根源を再生する</c.japanese>

229
00:13:58,587 --> 00:14:01,465
<font color="japanese">一度 受けた攻撃にしか使えぬがな</c.japanese>

230
00:14:04,260 --> 00:14:06,971
<font color="japanese">クククッ… いいだろう</c.japanese>

231
00:14:07,179 --> 00:14:09,932
<font color="japanese">この手で じかに
貴様を滅ぼせるのだ</c.japanese>

232
00:14:10,057 --> 00:14:13,435
<font color="japanese">むしろ よみがえってくれて
感謝しようというものだ</c.japanese>

233
00:14:13,561 --> 00:14:15,312
<font color="japanese">なあ 暴虐の魔王</c.japanese>

234
00:14:15,521 --> 00:14:18,065
<font color="japanese">聞け アゼシオンの民よ</c.japanese>

235
00:14:18,190 --> 00:14:21,735
<font color="japanese">今 深き暗黒が
この地を飲み込もうとしている</c.japanese>

236
00:14:21,861 --> 00:14:24,071
<font color="japanese">だが 恐れることはない</c.japanese>

237
00:14:24,196 --> 00:14:26,490
<font color="japanese">希望と共に祈りをささげよ</c.japanese>

238
00:14:26,615 --> 00:14:30,077
<font color="japanese">されば 光が暗黒を晴らすであろう</c.japanese>

239
00:14:30,369 --> 00:14:32,079
<font color="japanese">（勇者兵）暗黒がー！</c.japanese>

240
00:14:32,329 --> 00:14:34,415
<font color="japanese">（勇者兵）来るな！　来るなー！</c.japanese>

241
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:35,875
<font color="japanese">（アノス）愚かな</c.japanese>

242
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:39,503
<font color="japanese">無理やり希望を吸い取れば
民の心は二度と戻らぬぞ</c.japanese>

243
00:14:39,712 --> 00:14:42,089
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）これは
我が身を犠牲にしてまで―</c.japanese>

244
00:14:42,214 --> 00:14:45,092
<font color="japanese">貴様を滅ぼそうという尊い決意だ</c.japanese>

245
00:14:45,551 --> 00:14:47,803
<font color="japanese">聖なる正義の力を…</c.japanese>

246
00:14:47,928 --> 00:14:50,806
<font color="japanese">思い知るがいい！</c.japanese>

247
00:14:51,891 --> 00:14:52,725
<font color="japanese">むっ…</c.japanese>

248
00:14:54,768 --> 00:14:56,228
<font color="japanese">いくぞ 友よ</c.japanese>

249
00:14:56,353 --> 00:14:59,565
<font color="japanese">長きにわたる憎悪の連鎖
ここで断ち切る</c.japanese>

250
00:14:59,899 --> 00:15:03,527
<font color="japanese">ああ アゼシオンと
ディルヘイドに平和を</c.japanese>

251
00:15:06,530 --> 00:15:09,116
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）おぞましい妄想が！</c.japanese>

252
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:14,663
<font color="japanese">（レイ）はあーっ！</c.japanese>

253
00:15:15,998 --> 00:15:17,458
<font color="japanese">ぐあーっ！</c.japanese>

254
00:15:20,961 --> 00:15:22,338
<font color="japanese">ゾーラ･エ･ディプト</c.japanese>

255
00:15:25,549 --> 00:15:26,550
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）滅せよ！</c.japanese>

256
00:15:33,057 --> 00:15:34,433
<font color="japanese">フフフ…</c.japanese>

257
00:15:34,558 --> 00:15:37,227
<font color="japanese">よみがえったはいいが
傷は深かろう</c.japanese>

258
00:15:37,353 --> 00:15:39,939
<font color="japanese">もう魔力も ほとんど残っていまい</c.japanese>

259
00:15:40,272 --> 00:15:42,942
<font color="japanese">この身は もはや世界の法則</c.japanese>

260
00:15:43,067 --> 00:15:45,152
<font color="japanese">殺すことなど できはしない</c.japanese>

261
00:15:45,486 --> 00:15:47,863
<font color="japanese">世界の法則になったぐらいで</c.japanese>

262
00:15:47,988 --> 00:15:49,990
<font color="japanese">俺が従うとでも思ったか？</c.japanese>

263
00:15:50,115 --> 00:15:50,950
<font color="japanese">アスク</c.japanese>

264
00:15:51,283 --> 00:15:52,242
<font color="japanese">ファンユニオン</c.japanese>

265
00:15:52,743 --> 00:15:54,078
<font color="japanese">（マイア）ハッ… アノス様！</c.japanese>

266
00:15:54,203 --> 00:15:55,204
<font color="japanese">（アノス）歌え</c.japanese>

267
00:15:55,329 --> 00:15:58,916
<font color="japanese">あわれな亡霊に
レクイエムを聴かせてやれ</c.japanese>

268
00:15:59,041 --> 00:16:00,042
<font color="japanese">（ファンユニオン）はい！</c.japanese>

269
00:16:15,599 --> 00:16:21,230
<font color="japanese">♪「アノス様応援歌合唱曲第四番
《世界が愛に満ちるように》」</c.japanese>

270
00:16:50,509 --> 00:16:53,178
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）
聖なる魔法を愚弄するか</c.japanese>

271
00:16:53,303 --> 00:16:55,014
<font color="japanese">思い知るがいい</c.japanese>

272
00:16:55,139 --> 00:16:58,225
<font color="japanese">人間の恨み 決して消えぬ憎悪</c.japanese>

273
00:16:58,350 --> 00:17:00,144
<font color="japanese">それこそが アスクだ！</c.japanese>

274
00:17:11,739 --> 00:17:14,199
<font color="japanese">早く逃げて！
長くは もたないぞ！</c.japanese>

275
00:17:17,619 --> 00:17:20,247
<font color="japanese">（エリオ）アゼシオンの
負傷兵は 我らが避難させる</c.japanese>

276
00:17:20,372 --> 00:17:21,373
<font color="japanese">構わぬな！</c.japanese>

277
00:17:21,582 --> 00:17:24,084
<font color="japanese">でも 早く逃げないと君たちまで！</c.japanese>

278
00:17:24,543 --> 00:17:28,672
<font color="japanese">（エリオ）2000年前
偉大なる始祖は魔族のために戦った</c.japanese>

279
00:17:28,922 --> 00:17:32,301
<font color="japanese">今 ここにきて
誰が偽物で誰が本物か―</c.japanese>

280
00:17:32,968 --> 00:17:35,679
<font color="japanese">気付かぬほど私も鈍くはない</c.japanese>

281
00:17:35,971 --> 00:17:37,723
<font color="japanese">始祖の真意は明白</c.japanese>

282
00:17:37,848 --> 00:17:41,351
<font color="japanese">我ら魔王の末えいの
今こそ忠義を示すとき！</c.japanese>

283
00:17:41,477 --> 00:17:42,311
<font color="japanese">（魔王兵たち）はっ！</c.japanese>

284
00:17:45,981 --> 00:17:51,695
<font color="japanese">（ファンユニオンの歌声）</c.japanese>

285
00:18:26,772 --> 00:18:29,108
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）
魔族が こしゃくなマネを！</c.japanese>

286
00:18:29,483 --> 00:18:32,069
<font color="japanese">ぐあっ ああー！</c.japanese>

287
00:18:32,402 --> 00:18:34,113
<font color="japanese">（アノス）見えぬか ジェルガ</c.japanese>

288
00:18:34,238 --> 00:18:36,532
<font color="japanese">人間と魔族が手を取り合い―</c.japanese>

289
00:18:36,657 --> 00:18:39,076
<font color="japanese">必死で生きようとする姿が</c.japanese>

290
00:18:39,201 --> 00:18:40,994
<font color="japanese">時代は とうに変わった</c.japanese>

291
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,913
<font color="japanese">世界は平和になったのだ</c.japanese>

292
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:44,289
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）平和だと!?</c.japanese>

293
00:18:44,414 --> 00:18:47,793
<font color="japanese">そんなものは貴様が2000年前に
ぶち壊しただろう！</c.japanese>

294
00:18:47,918 --> 00:18:49,753
<font color="japanese">これは復讐なのだ</c.japanese>

295
00:18:49,878 --> 00:18:52,756
<font color="japanese">魔族を滅ぼすまで決して終わらぬ！</c.japanese>

296
00:18:53,006 --> 00:18:54,758
<font color="japanese">（アノス）愚かな男だ</c.japanese>

297
00:18:54,883 --> 00:18:56,301
<font color="japanese">お前に残されたのは―</c.japanese>

298
00:18:56,426 --> 00:18:58,345
<font color="japanese">決して 恨みだけでは
なかったはずだ</c.japanese>

299
00:18:58,512 --> 00:19:00,305
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）愚かなのは貴様だ</c.japanese>

300
00:19:00,430 --> 00:19:02,182
<font color="japanese">ジェルガは世界の法則</c.japanese>

301
00:19:02,307 --> 00:19:05,727
<font color="japanese">この世界から決して消えぬ
人間の憎悪</c.japanese>

302
00:19:05,853 --> 00:19:08,981
<font color="japanese">魔族が滅びることは宿命なのだ！</c.japanese>

303
00:19:09,106 --> 00:19:10,107
<font color="japanese">（レイ）だったら…</c.japanese>

304
00:19:10,816 --> 00:19:14,027
<font color="japanese">その宿命を断ち切るのが
勇者の役目だ</c.japanese>

305
00:19:14,153 --> 00:19:15,737
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）なぜ… なぜだ！</c.japanese>

306
00:19:15,863 --> 00:19:19,658
<font color="japanese">エヴァンスマナが私の宿命を
断ち切れるわけが…</c.japanese>

307
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,703
<font color="japanese">（アノス）そのことわりを滅ぼした</c.japanese>

308
00:19:23,912 --> 00:19:26,373
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガ）デルゾゲードだと？</c.japanese>

309
00:19:26,707 --> 00:19:29,501
<font color="japanese">人間が魔族を憎んだのではない</c.japanese>

310
00:19:29,626 --> 00:19:31,461
<font color="japanese">お前が俺を憎んだのだ</c.japanese>

311
00:19:32,129 --> 00:19:34,631
<font color="japanese">ならば 最後まで１人でやれ</c.japanese>

312
00:19:38,260 --> 00:19:41,013
<font color="japanese">地獄の底まで つきあってやる</c.japanese>

313
00:19:42,514 --> 00:19:44,057
<font color="japanese">させぬ！</c.japanese>

314
00:19:44,183 --> 00:19:46,476
<font color="japanese">させぬぞー！</c.japanese>

315
00:19:59,907 --> 00:20:05,746
<font color="japanese">（ファンユニオンの歌声）</c.japanese>

316
00:20:12,502 --> 00:20:17,507
<font color="japanese">（ジェルガのうめき声）</c.japanese>

317
00:20:18,425 --> 00:20:23,430
<font color="japanese">（ファンユニオンの歌声）</c.japanese>

318
00:20:50,290 --> 00:20:51,959
<font color="japanese">アノス！</c.japanese>

319
00:20:51,959 --> 00:20:52,167
<font color="japanese">アノス！</c.japanese>

320
00:20:51,959 --> 00:20:52,167
{\an8}<font color="japanese">♪～</c.japanese>

321
00:20:52,167 --> 00:20:54,336
{\an8}<font color="japanese">♪～</c.japanese>

322
00:20:54,962 --> 00:20:56,755
<font color="japanese">（サーシャ）
びっくりさせないでよね！</c.japanese>

323
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,882
<font color="japanese">ほんとに死んだかと思ったわ</c.japanese>

324
00:20:59,007 --> 00:21:00,676
<font color="japanese">（ミーシャ）心配した…</c.japanese>

325
00:21:00,801 --> 00:21:03,679
<font color="japanese">泣くな 俺が死ぬわけなかろう</c.japanese>

326
00:21:04,304 --> 00:21:05,430
<font color="japanese">（２人）ううっ…</c.japanese>

327
00:21:18,819 --> 00:21:19,820
<font color="japanese">（レイ）ごめん</c.japanese>

328
00:21:21,238 --> 00:21:22,739
<font color="japanese">おかえりなさい</c.japanese>

329
00:21:24,157 --> 00:21:25,367
<font color="japanese">（レイ）ただいま</c.japanese>

330
00:21:32,374 --> 00:21:33,709
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（アノス）エレオノール</c.japanese>

331
00:21:34,626 --> 00:21:35,794
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（エレオノール）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">アノス君…</c.japanese>

332
00:21:35,919 --> 00:21:37,421
{\an8}<font color="japanese">約束を果たそう</c.japanese>

333
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:42,592
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（エレオノール）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">これって…</c.japanese>

334
00:21:42,718 --> 00:21:44,970
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（アノス）お前を</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">俺の魔法にした</c.japanese>

335
00:21:45,262 --> 00:21:47,639
{\an8}<font color="japanese">これで悪用されることは</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">あるまい</c.japanese>

336
00:21:49,308 --> 00:21:52,644
{\an8}<font color="japanese">１万人のゼシアも</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">面倒を見てやらねばな</c.japanese>

337
00:21:53,103 --> 00:21:56,606
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（エレオノールの</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">泣き声）</c.japanese>

338
00:21:57,316 --> 00:21:59,818
{\an8}<font color="japanese">ありがとう アノス君</c.japanese>

339
00:22:02,487 --> 00:22:03,864
{\an8}<font color="japanese">大好きだぞ</c.japanese>

340
00:22:23,383 --> 00:22:28,388
{\an8}<font color="japanese">～♪</c.japanese>

341
00:22:31,016 --> 00:22:32,225
<font color="japanese">（イザベラ）アノスちゃん！</c.japanese>

342
00:22:32,642 --> 00:22:34,019
<font color="japanese">ただいま 母さん</c.japanese>

343
00:22:34,144 --> 00:22:37,481
<font color="japanese">（イザベラ）心配したのよ
戦争って聞いて…</c.japanese>

344
00:22:37,606 --> 00:22:39,441
<font color="japanese">（グスタ）大丈夫だったか アノス</c.japanese>

345
00:22:39,566 --> 00:22:41,568
<font color="japanese">ああ 戦争なら俺が…</c.japanese>

346
00:22:41,693 --> 00:22:43,111
<font color="japanese">（グスタ）なっ… 待て！</c.japanese>

347
00:22:43,278 --> 00:22:47,157
<font color="japanese">お… お前 その女の子は
も… もしかして…</c.japanese>

348
00:22:47,324 --> 00:22:50,786
<font color="japanese">アノスちゃん またお嫁さん
増やしちゃったの～!?</c.japanese>

349
00:22:50,911 --> 00:22:53,705
<font color="japanese">ち… 違うぞ！
ボクは アノス君の…</c.japanese>

350
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:54,831
<font color="japanese">そ… そう</c.japanese>

351
00:22:54,956 --> 00:22:57,250
<font color="japanese">お前を俺の魔法にしたって
言われて…</c.japanese>

352
00:22:57,501 --> 00:23:00,003
<font color="japanese">お前を俺の魔法にした…</c.japanese>

353
00:23:00,170 --> 00:23:03,590
<font color="japanese">お前 ついに
そんなしゃれたプロポーズまで…</c.japanese>

354
00:23:03,965 --> 00:23:06,176
<font color="japanese">（エレオノール）
えっと… え？　えっと…</c.japanese>

355
00:23:06,635 --> 00:23:09,596
<font color="japanese">これで 子供が
１万人いるって言ったら…</c.japanese>

356
00:23:09,721 --> 00:23:10,889
<font color="japanese">卒倒しちゃう</c.japanese>

357
00:23:11,014 --> 00:23:12,099
<font color="japanese">（２人）なああっ！</c.japanese>

358
00:23:12,224 --> 00:23:13,767
<font color="japanese">お… おじいちゃん…</c.japanese>

359
00:23:13,975 --> 00:23:14,893
<font color="japanese">（イザベラ）むん！</c.japanese>

360
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:19,064
<font color="japanese">ちょっと中で 詳しく
話を聞かせてもらえるかな～？</c.japanese>

361
00:23:19,189 --> 00:23:20,357
<font color="japanese">う… うん</c.japanese>

362
00:23:20,482 --> 00:23:22,984
{\an5}<font color="japanese">（イザベラ）
サーシャちゃん ミーシャちゃんも
ごはん食べていくでしょ？</c.japanese>

363
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:23,944
<font color="japanese">（２人）はい</c.japanese>

364
00:23:24,486 --> 00:23:25,403
<font color="japanese">フッ…</c.japanese>

365
00:23:26,446 --> 00:23:27,989
<font color="japanese">キノコグラタンはあるか？</c.japanese>

366
00:23:28,115 --> 00:23:29,116
<font color="japanese">（イザベラ）もっちろ～ん！</c.japanese>

367
00:23:29,241 --> 00:23:31,409
<font color="japanese">そう言うと思って
たっぷり作ってあるわ</c.japanese>

368
00:23:31,535 --> 00:23:33,078
<font color="japanese">かわいいお嫁さんが３人</c.japanese>

369
00:23:33,203 --> 00:23:34,746
<font color="japanese">そして孫が１万人！</c.japanese>

370
00:23:34,871 --> 00:23:37,874
<font color="japanese">忙しくなるわ～ アハハッ！</c.japanese>

371
00:23:37,999 --> 00:23:40,001
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（アノス）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">ああ そうだな</c.japanese>

